FBIS4-67008 "jptdd019__l94070" JPRS-TDD-94-019-L JPRS Narcotics 26 April 1994 EAST EUROPE BULGARIA Customs Seizes 24 Kg of Heroin at Kapitan Andreevo Checkpoint Customs Seizes 24 Kg of Heroin at Kapitan Andreevo Checkpoint AU2604183594 Sofia BTA in English 1708 GMT 26 Apr 94 AU2604183594 Sofia BTA English BFN [Text] Khaskovo, April 26 (BTA) -- Customs officers at the Kapitan Andreevo border checkpoint (on the Bulgarian-Turkish border) prevented the smuggling of 24 kg of heroin, the local BTA correspondent reported. The drug-trafficker is a Pole travelling from Turkey to Poland in a BMW car. The narcotic was found in 92 packets in a secret compartment behind the back seat of the car.
